message.text:
#TamAnunsyo | As of today, September 17, 2025, Far Eastern University has officially announced that FEU Manila and Makati students with scheduled onsite and laboratory classes every Thursday and Friday will follow different learning modalities on September 18 and 19, depending on their Institute.

Be reminded that facilities including the Main Library, Shared Hybrid Learning Spaces, and the Huddle will stay open for onsite services and student utilization.

Stay updated through our Tam Anunsyo. 

Source: Far Eastern University 

#TamaRiseTogether 
#FEUCSO90

Be reminded that facilities including the Main Library, Shared Hybrid Learning Spaces, and the Huddle will stay open for onsite services and student utilization.

Stay updated through our Tam Anunsyo. 

Source: Far Eastern University

message.text:
#TamAnunsyo | As of today, September 17, 2025, Far Eastern University has officially announced that FEU Manila and Makati students with scheduled onsite and laboratory classes every Thursday and Friday will follow different learning modalities on September 18 and 19, depending on their Institute.

Be reminded that facilities including the Main Library, Shared Hybrid Learning Spaces, and the Huddle will stay open for onsite services and student utilization.

Stay updated through our Tam Anunsyo. 

Source: Far Eastern University 

#TamaRiseTogether 
#FEUCSO90

media.accessibility_caption: May be a graphic of text that says 'ADVISORY In view of the transport strike, FEU Manila and Makati students with scheduled onsite and laboratory classes every Thursday and Friday will follow different learning modalities on September 18 and 19, depending on their Institute. ITHM, IE Continue with onsite laboratory classes. Students affected by the transport strike may avail of the Accommodation Policy. IHSN, IABF, IARFA, IAS to consult their teachers for specific instructions. Shift to online classes. Students are advised Offices, including the Main Library, Shared Hybrid Learning Spaces, and The Huddle, will remain open for onsite transactions and student use. FEU'
